{"tid":89402,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"丸久小山園 $200 一條卷蛋 昆人 實錄 港豬慘被騙","createTime":"2017-01-21T10:20:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T06:10:06.000Z","uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6804045688a31fcd12f0aa613ab48849e1be1ce7","tid":89402,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:20:27.000Z","msg":"15:49更新我們剛託京都市國際觀光大使致電去小山園查詢，得到的回覆香港「丸久小山園」所販賣的已包裝商品，的確是跟小山園合作販賣的，但是關於咖啡店，即現場享用的蛋糕或點心等，是香港那邊自行開始販賣的，卻未有經過小山園同意。對於這件事情目前要怎麼處理，他們公司內部目前還在商討中。<br />\n<br />\n京都西洞院店長表示知道香港有向他們入貨，但並沒有授權他們使用商標。因此正在和律師商討如何處理，並將於今天5時在官網發出聲明。<br />\n<br />\n近日鬧出香港的「丸久小山園」非為日本官方授權，事源星期二台灣網民「日本抹茶&amp;甜點-漂流抹茶海，沉溺甜點鄉」去信日本本店，問及香港店的事宜。當時本店的回覆丸久小山園未有海外分店。他在Facebook的帖中更三番四次表明香港並沒有取得正式許可，不少留言者亦表示憤怒及失望。<br />\n<br />\n我們即時查問香港店的負責人廖傑民先生，他表示香港店並未有盜用「丸久小山園」的商標，當初亦有與日本官方簽定合約，屬於官方授權的海外加盟店。然而香港店的確非為日本方直接管理，而是交由香港第三方代為管理，因此店舖的商標下亦寫有「Managed by」的字眼。負責人表示他們最快星期一會聯同日本代表發出聯合聲明。我們會為大家密切跟進事態的發展。"},{"pid":"f20d7f2260e196380b89f0018193ac42ea1b4c0a","tid":89402,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:26:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aa2dba28497d4ee0475169c3dce370f5fa145c7","tid":89402,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:22:38.000Z","msg":"之前都好似試過係咁，咁搞法香港個名遲早臭"},{"pid":"787c4d833ffc471bd538e1aa77f1bcf917a0a6b3","tid":89402,"uid":36178,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:25:33.000Z","msg":"支那人？"},{"pid":"720ff6df4d54aac0c4b5594b510afce9b2e1ca4f","tid":89402,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:26:13.000Z","msg":"台狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97334bb4a4c941a79d28b2de68faaffb3c445deb","tid":89402,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:57:28.000Z","msg":"應該係香港間鋪同日本買話去香港賣，之後唔問人地，用埋人地個商標做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"508ae42668d0978b0fbefaec303a10d6b378d74f","tid":89402,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:57:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>應該係香港間鋪同日本買貨話去香港賣，之後唔問人地，用埋人地個商標做生意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"78080552f264fa2e125f157b1699b57bbcf2d447","tid":89402,"uid":17646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:07:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73d37c4b9b35f3e0c50b9f6858f4390f49b7fd53","tid":89402,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"借鼓油賣雞，咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"664011e18706c8228bfd39050c10da090e31202c","tid":89402,"uid":61105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:14:55.000Z","msg":"好彩無即刻去食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2681ab342cbfd1c4895ccec2da0b2e9a276d6379","tid":89402,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T12:51:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>借鼓油賣雞，咁好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n入貨 變左 分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35e976178efd879d3e5e06bb9ee1befe96e2e9ca","tid":89402,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T13:54:15.000Z","msg":"成件事感覺好大陸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2915d